QuestData.Title: WANTED: Keeho's Severed Paw
QuestData.Description: Posted by: Lieutenant Willem$B$BKeeho, a monstrous saberon, has taken to raiding Southport at night. We're losing men left and right.$B$BI offer a hefty bounty to anyone able to track down Kreeho and bring his severed paw to me.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve Keeho's Severed Paw from Keeho the Savage.
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, commander. For the Alliance!
